    <div class="inner-block">
      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Warren Tucker is currently a Non-Executive Director of Reckitt Benckiser Plc, Thomas Cook Group Plc and Survitec Group Limited.</p>

<p>Warren is a qualified Chartered Accountant, MBA and an experienced CFO. He serves on the audit committees of all these companies, currently chairing one audit committee and one remuneration committee.</p>

<p>After a series of financial roles at British Airways Plc and Cable & Wireless Plc, Warren was appointed CFO for Cobham Plc where he served as an Executive Director on the Board for over 10 years until 2013.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_3068">
            <h1 id="non-executive-director">Non Executive Director</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Board members give corporate leadership to the <abbr title="Foreign & Commonwealth Office">FCO</abbr> by ensuring that the department meets the foreign policy priorities, Public Service Agreements targets and service delivery targets set by ministers. The role of a Non-Executive Board Member is to provide an effective and objective challenge to the rest of the Board and officials.</p>

</div>
